Version: 0.2.0
Release-Focus: Major bugfixes

Added new examples for new API.  Documentation improvements, e.g., API
manual in DevHelp format.  Update of gnulib files.  More self tests.
Translation fixes.  The EXTERNAL mechanism now support authorization
identities.  Major internal overhaul of the library, to remove all
fixed size buffers in the API, and to simplify the callback interface.
Update of generic crypto layer.  It is now possible to add a new SASL
mechanism during run-time.  A few memory leaks fixed.  Libtool's
-export-symbols-regex is now used to only export official APIs.
